    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320400/extras/5583d56217603668273230a69d604cbf.avif?t=1749564570\" width=630 height=180 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320400/extras/9a40e0d6b070dfaf3d7b9de2582cb911.webp?t=1749564570\" width=620 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以英勇之姿与无上荣耀，持全新精选火器，昂然踏上《坚守》的战场。这些火器拥有全新模型和精致纹饰，让你在队伍中脱颖而出。从诺克枪到运动步枪，武器包应有尽有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黑火药火器》包默认解锁6把全新独特火器。此外，通过完成6项全新力量挑战，还可额外解锁6把装饰版火器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《坚守》DLC中的内容纯属外观装饰，永远不会影响游戏玩法。你们的慷慨支持将推动我们钟爱的角色扮演战争游戏受到更多关注。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320400/extras/ec52de48616dcaf0d28b053be0dab20e.webp?t=1749564570\" width=620 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁布泰滑膛枪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁装饰版布泰滑膛枪成就“千钧一发”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁奥斯曼图芬克滑膛枪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁装饰版奥斯曼图芬克滑膛枪成就“厄运难逃”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁诺克枪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁装饰版诺克枪成就“诺克惊魂”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁运动卡宾枪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁装饰版运动卡宾枪成就“卡宾装填”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁运动步枪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁装饰版运动步枪成就“膛线猎手”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁勒帕热手枪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁装饰版勒帕热手枪成就“狂暴勒帕热”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 解锁“双关大师”头像，可展示在你的玩家名片上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320400/extras/a0cfb0f8f8bce321cb98f6f17f93a9e4.webp?t=1749564570\" width=630 height=36 /></span></p>",
